  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育平台设计一个完整的访问架构图。核心是学生数据库Education_StudentDB作为入口，然后经过Route 53的DNS解析，最终落到我们的LMS门户存储系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以StudentDB在这里既是用户入口，又作为数据存储？还有DNS部分我打算用子图来包裹R53节点，命名为Education_GradeSync，这样符合你的设计意图吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "R53"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，R53放在GradeSync子图里。不过StudentDB确实身兼两职——既是入口标识，CDN层也会有一个同名的边缘节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "EDGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那我构建CDN子图，命名为Education_ContentCDN。里面需要包含边缘节点、Lambda函数、证书管理和缓存层。这些组件分别对应ClassroomService和GradeSync的实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CDN",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "ContentCDN的结构没问题。Lambda和Cache都用ClassroomService，证书管理用GradeSync。连接顺序应该是边缘到Lambda，再到证书，最后到缓存。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加CDN子图及其内部四个节点。现在处理存储层——STORAGE子图命名为Education_LMS_Portal，包含OAI和FILES两个GradeSync节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STORAGE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "连接关系需要仔细处理。USER到R53走HTTPS，然后R53指向EDGE，CDN内部链式串联，最后CACHE到OAI要标注\"OAI Only\"，OAI再连到FILES。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "CACHE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "所有连接已绘制完成，包括HTTPS标签和OAI Only标注。现在为各子图添加颜色区分——USER用蓝色系，DNS用琥珀色，CDN用粉色，STORAGE用绿色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "style"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "颜色方案可以，但让我确认一下层级关系。DNS子图里的R53是直接暴露给USER的，这个理解正确吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "R53"
